place.name: KETTLE
place.gazetteerText: Kettle, par. and vil. with ry. sta. (Kingskettle), Fife, on river Eden - par., 7612 ac., pop. 2054; vil., 1 m. S. of Ladybank Junction, pop. 598; P.O., T.O.; 1 mile S. of Kettle is Kettlebridge (or Holekettle), vil., pop. 451. (In 1887, John Bartholomew's Gazetteer of the British Isles)
